  "prompt": "How can I retrieve my WeChat account if I've forgotten my password, I just linked my linked & I remember I wechat ID.But I don't have QQ/phone linked?",
  "response": "If you've forgotten your WeChat password and you do not have a QQ account or a phone number linked, you can still attempt to recover your account by following these steps:\n\n1. **Open WeChat**: Launch the WeChat app on your device.\n\n2. **Go to Login Page**: On the login screen, click on \"Forget password?\"\n\n3. **Select Recovery Method**: Since you mentioned you\u2019ve linked your WeChat ID, choose the option that allows you to recover your account using your WeChat ID.\n\n4. **Account Verification**: You may be prompted to verify your identity. Follow the on-screen instructions. This may include answering security questions, if you've set them up.\n\n5. **Follow Instructions**: If you can verify your identity successfully, you will be guided through the process to reset your password.\n\n6. **Check for Account Recovery Options**: If you do not see a method that works for you, look for an option to contact WeChat support. You might need to provide information that proves you are the owner of the account.\n\n7. **Wait for Assistance**: If you contact support, wait for their response for further assistance.\n\nIf you've exhausted all options and cannot recover your account, it may be necessary to create a new WeChat account. Be sure to keep your contact methods updated to avoid similar issues in the future.",
